OL,3,CReligious hate crimes in England and
OL,4,CWales hit record high
OL,6,FReligious hate crimes recorded by
OL,7,Fpolice in England and Wales have hit a
OL,8,Frecord high, new Home Office figures
OL,9,Fshow.
OL,11,FIn the year to March, there were 7,164
OL,12,Fsuch offences recorded by forces
OL,13,Facross the two nations ` excluding the
OL,14,FMetropolitan Police - an increase of
OL,15,F3% from 6,973 in the previous 12
OL,16,Fmonths.
OL,18,FThis was the highest annual total of
OL,19,Freligious hate crimes recorded, the
OL,20,FHome Office said.
