OL,3,CReligious hate crimes in England and
OL,4,CWales hit record high
OL,6,FReligious hate crimes targeted at
OL,7,FMuslims in England and Wales increased
OL,8,Fby 19% in the past year - from 2,690
OL,9,Fto 3,199 - with a spike in offences
OL,10,Ffollowing the Southport murders, the
OL,11,Freport said.
OL,13,FThe increase was driven by the
OL,14,Fprotests and unrest the week after
OL,15,Fthree children were stabbed to death
OL,16,Fin Southport on July 29 last year,
OL,17,Fwhile attending a Taylor Swift dance
OL,18,Fclass during the summer holidays.
