OL,3,CReligious hate crimes in England and
OL,4,CWales hit record high
OL,6,FA day after the attack, riots broke
OL,7,Fout on the streets of Southport, and
OL,8,Fwithin six days, violence had spread
OL,9,Fto more than 30 towns and cities, with
OL,10,Fmore than 1,000 arrests in the weeks
OL,11,Fthat followed.
OL,13,FThe protests were fuelled by false
OL,14,Fclaims on social media that the
OL,15,Fperpetrator was a Muslim and an asylum
OL,16,Fseeker, triggering racist attacks and
OL,17,Fanti-immigration marches, and leading
OL,18,Fmany to brand the protestors as far
OL,19,Fright and racist.
